          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "The day starts in a nice and lazy way. I still have yet to buy more coffee - why are you doing this to yourself, Leo? - so I put Milo, Jakobs and honey into a cup and call it good enough. I nail the amount of oats and it’s pretty spectacular.",
